leonardo carrera gómez (born june 9, 1961) is a mexican professional wrestler best known under the name damián 666. he has worked for world championship wrestling (wcw), consejo mundial de lucha libre (cmll), asistencia asesoría y administración (aaa), world wrestling association (wwa) and various promotions on the mexican independent circuit, including perros del mal producciones. carrera also worked under the ring name galaxy in wcw, a masked luchador. carrera often team with halloween, forming the team "mexico's most wanted" which has worked extensively in north america for such promotions as xtreme pro wrestling (xpw) and revolution pro. carrera's son currently wrestles for perros del mal as bestia 666.